{
  "stem": "26728.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there are thousands, and they were shot and they were gassed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a working gas chamber at Mauthausen, which Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wiesenthal and I got into a hell of an argument about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he was in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was an inmate in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The argument was-- he made a statement, which has been quoted by the revisionists and deniers that there were no death camps on German soil during World War II.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he did not-- he classified-- a death camp, by his definition, was Auschwitz, Treblinka, Cherno.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were death camps, and they were all in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in reality, Auschwitz was not in Poland, it was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, Germany had annexed that territory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, there's a lot of hair splitting going on about these kind of things, so it's not really germane.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a working gas chamber at Mauthausen and they-- every kind of torture imaginable had taken place in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mass starvation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mass-- One device at Mauthausen that I saw myself, and I couldn't imagine dying like this, was a little closet not big enough for three people, let's say four people max, four adults.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Solid walls, four solid walls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Small ceiling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You crawled in through on a brick opening about this far from the floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You crawled in and four men got in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No openings.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they sealed the crawl space where you crawled in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was-- then you stayed in there for 48 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You couldn't move, you couldn't turn, you were body to body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Pressed in like in an elevator, only much smaller.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if you survived, when they got you out, when they opened it up through the bottom-- you couldn't even-- if you died, you couldn't even fall down.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
